  <title>Cogl.buffer_set_data</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function buffer_set_data(buffer: <link xref="Cogl.Buffer">Cogl.Buffer</link>, offset: Number(gsize), data: void, size: Number(gsize)): <link xref="Cogl.Bool">Cogl.Bool</link> {
    // Gjs wrapper for cogl_buffer_set_data()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Updates part of the buffer with new data from <code>data</code>. Where to put this new
data is controlled by <code>offset</code> and <code>offset</code> + <code>data</code> should be less than the
buffer size.</p>
  <p>Since 1.2</p>
